那么，让我们从一些基础知识开始

00:03:19.896 --> 00:03:25.906 A:middle
If you're coming over from iOS, note that on Apple TV,
如果你来自于iOS，注意在 Apple TV 上，

00:03:25.906 --> 00:03:29.526 A:middle
