你界面中的所有东西都需要大一码

00:04:46.706 --> 00:04:48.946 A:middle
And that's starting with graphics.
从图像开始

00:04:49.896 --> 00:04:52.626 A:middle
Both graphics and your user interface elements such as,
无论是图片还是你的界面元素，比如

00:04:52.726 --> 00:04:55.286 A:middle
buttons or controls need to be larger
按钮和控件，都必须更大一些

00:04:55.286 --> 00:04:57.426 A:middle
so they can be easily seen from across the room.
这样它们才能在整个房间里都很容易看到

